{"id":239526,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-山东莱州访民遭殴打后被拘留10天（图）/","date":"2012-07-12T18:16:10Z","modified":"2012-07-12T18:16:10Z","title":"维权网 | 山东莱州访民遭殴打后被拘留10天（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span> </span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><br /><span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员姜维泉报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>点钟，山东莱州访民郝卫英被当地警方叫到派出所，说是与日前殴打她丈夫的人一块协调解决问题，郝卫英在派出所外面等待结果。晚上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>点多钟，派出所以双方打架斗殴为名，对郝卫英丈夫王某处以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天拘留，打人者郝佳佳处以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>天拘留。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>山东莱州访民郝卫英</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>号在北京上访时被当地政府抓回（维权网前期有报道）。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>号，郝卫英称村委指使村民郝佳佳殴打其丈夫王某，致使王某脑震荡，门牙被打断，多处皮外伤，住院一个多月，医学鉴定为轻微伤。郝卫英多次报案，要求处理。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>结果今天下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>点钟，当地警方召集双方到派出所解决问题，却将打人与被打者同时拘留。依照法律，打人致轻微伤属于刑事犯罪，当追究法律责任。当地警方以行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>天来以罚代罪，并且将被打者也同时拘留，显然违反法律。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>郝卫英对此结果强烈不满，受害者当时被凶手殴打时只是招架，并无还手，也没有造成郝佳佳任何伤害。郝卫英称郝佳佳的一名亲戚徐海生原在莱州公安局任政委，去年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月调任龙口市公安局任局长，在此案中疑利用关系袒护凶手。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当地派出所所长孙某在接受外界电话查询时以不了解对方身份为由，拒绝谈及本案任何情况。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>郝卫英电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18353542752</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-tKefpa1tnv0/T_71GvO7YvI/AAAAAAAAJN0/eYder3gszGI/s1600/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+018.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-tKefpa1tnv0/T_71GvO7YvI/AAAAAAAAJN0/eYder3gszGI/s320/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+018.jpg\" width=\"224\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-qrQRRXioy4s/T_71L-G5DAI/AAAAAAAAJN8/RkP2XDzmmSE/s1600/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+019.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-qrQRRXioy4s/T_71L-G5DAI/AAAAAAAAJN8/RkP2XDzmmSE/s320/%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87+019.jpg\" width=\"216\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-4151650471901681066?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/e3bcdc6f78987018.jpg-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}